import { library } from '@fortawesome/fontawesome-svg-core'
import {
  faCog,
  faSignOutAlt,
  faHome,
  faTachometerAlt,
  faPencilRuler,
  faFile,
  faRss,
  faFolderOpen,
  faImage,
  faCogs,
  faUser,
  faAngleDown,
  faBars,
  faQuestionCircle,
  faMinusCircle,
  faPlusCircle
} from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons'

import {
  faInstagram,
  faLinkedinIn,
  faGithub
} from '@fortawesome/free-brands-svg-icons'

// To add a new icon, append it to the import statement as well as the library.add() call
// Ex. to add the address-book icon, add faAddressBook
library.add(faCog,
  faSignOutAlt,
  faHome,
  faTachometerAlt,
  faPencilRuler,
  faFile,
  faRss,
  faFolderOpen,
  faImage,
  faCogs,
  faUser,
  faAngleDown,
  faBars,
  faQuestionCircle,
  faMinusCircle,
  faPlusCircle,
  faInstagram,
  faLinkedinIn,
  faGithub)
